Bolivia 1994

*First Stage
*Group A
* 1.Jorge Wilstermann       12  6  3  3  21-10  15  Qualified
* 2.Real Santa Cruz         12  6  3  3  15- 9  15  Qualified
* 3.Blooming                12  5  4  3  21-12  14
* 4.Bolívar                 12  5  3  4  19-18  14
