* 5.Guabirá                 12  4  3  5  15-18  11
* 6.Metalsan                12  1  1 10   9-29   3

Apertura Semifinals

First Legs
[May 14]
Jorge Wilstermann       4-0 San José
[May 15]
Independiente Petrolero 2-1 Real Santa Cruz

Second Legs
[May 21]
Real Santa Cruz         3-1 Independiente Petrolero
[May 22]
San José                4-0 Jorge Wilstermann

Independiente and Wilstermann qualified due to better group records (as both
ties finished equal on points if not goals)

Apertura Final

First Leg 
Jorge Wilstermann       3-1 Independiente Petrolero

Second Leg
Independiente Petrolero 1-0 Jorge Wilstermann

Playoff
Jorge Wilstermann       5-3 Independiente Petrolero


Second Stage

