Championship Playoff

 1.Bolívar                 10  6  3  1  21- 6  15
 2.Jorge Wilstermann       10  4  3  3  21-16  11
 3.The Strongest           10  3  4  3  11-17  10
 4.Independiente Petrolero 10  4  1  5  15-13   9
 5.Guabirá                 10  2  4  4   9-21   8
 6.Real Santa Cruz         10  1  5  4  10-14   7


Relegation:

Metalsan were relegated because of worst overall record.
Ciclón (2nd worst record) had to play off against Always Ready,
runners-up in the Torneo Simon Bolívar:

Ciclón 2-0 0-0 Always Ready.

Promoted: Stormers (winners Torneo Simon Bolívar).



